{"tid":2406142,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解籤師傅：車公認為政府抗疫舉棋不定　封區勞民傷財","createTime":"2021-02-13T03:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T10:59:02.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2ea6cee43e9b01878932b5dc867d3c823f13b6cb","tid":2406142,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:16:32.000Z","msg":"鄉議局主席劉業強在車公廟為香港求得第四十五籤的中籤，籤文是「下手須教一著先，世情局面苦徒然；積薪歷火非無事，識者能知火未燃」。<br />\n<br />\n解籤師傅陳天恩表示，車公認為政府抗疫措施舉棋不定，希望當局一氣呵成解決疫情，否則出現第5波、第6波疫情才知錯，經濟將更加會走下坡、市民會更惶恐。<br />\n<br />\n陳天恩又說，車公認為當局早前的封區措施勞民傷財，疫情只會無了期，最好是仿傚內地封城，全民檢測和禁足28日，才能完全控制疫情，經濟自然會復甦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575524-20210213.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575524-20210213.htm&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=39b07585\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575524-20210213.htm&h=1052bef2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575524-20210213.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4814ebe252e8c2c65148f00a21be27007a6d0670","tid":2406142,"uid":242537,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:17:21.000Z","msg":"籤黎架咋<br />\n唔係誠實豆沙包吖屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df67c1c6a8e04fbc1996f907b62099c18e027817","tid":2406142,"uid":337210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:21:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b2qdRT01r9k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb2qdRT01r9k&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ6VJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=61e5b697\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\"